This folder contains the lecture, paramters notes and codes to perform variant calling on a set of subsamples exome files using GATK best practices pipeline.
The sample data can be accessed via https://zenodo.org/records/3243160.

The data has been originally subsampled by 
Uva, P., & Cuccuru, G. (2016). Training material for the course "Exome analysis with GALAXY" [Data set]. Zenodo. https://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3243160

